org.domainobject.util.convert

Interface Manipulator<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the object to be manipulated
    All Superinterfaces:
    Converter<T,T>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Translator

    public interface Manipulator<T>
extends Converter<T,T>
    A callback interface defining the manipulation of object, without morhping it into another type of object. In goes an object, out comes another object of the same type, or the same object in another state.
